  <v-progress-circular v-if="isLoading" indeterminate></v-progress-circular>
  <v-menu v-else offset-y>
    <template v-slot:activator="{on, attrs}">
      <v-btn icon v-on="on" v-bind="attrs">
        <v-avatar color="accent" size="32">
          <v-icon>mdi-account</v-icon>
        </v-avatar>
      </v-btn>
    </template>
    <v-card>
      <v-card-text>
        <v-switch label="Dark Theme" :input-value="darkMode" @change="setDarkMode($event)"></v-switch>
      </v-card-text>
      <template>
        <v-card-actions>
          <v-btn to="/login" block color="primary">로그인</v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
        <v-card-actions>
          <v-btn to="/join" block color="secondary">회원가입</v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
      </template>
    </v-card>
  </v-menu>

</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "SiteUser",
  data(){
    return {
      isLoading : false,
    }
  },
  computed : {
    darkMode() {
      return this.$vuetify.theme.dark;
    }
  },
  mounted(){
    this.getDarkMode();
  },
  methods : {
    setDarkMode(mode){
      this.$vuetify.theme.dark = mode;
      localStorage.setItem('darkMode', mode ? 'dark' : 'light');
    },
    getDarkMode(){
      const mode = localStorage.getItem('darkMode') === 'dark' ? true : false;
      this.$vuetify.theme.dark = mode;
    }
  }
};
</script>
